<br>
Yes it is a Haste belt.  There are TONS of Haste belts in game.  FBSS.  Sash of the Dragonborn, Hangmans Noose.  Swirlspine Belt, Runebranded Girdle.  Runed Bolster Belt.<br>
<br>
Look at the other stats.  It has 10 AC, 4 Sta, and 5 Int/Wis.  That makes it the best belt in game for Int casters, bar none that I am aware of.  There are melee items which are more desirable for tanks.  From what I understand the Haste component on this item is nothing terribly special.<br>
<br>
If you are incapable of imagining someone rolling against you on this item, well, I am incapable of imagining a warrior rolling against me on a Heirophant Cloak too.  But it happens every day.  If the criterion is "Can and Will Use" then the Silvery Belt would DEFINITELY be an item a Int caster (especially an Enchanter -- we like AC items 'cos we get pounded a lot) would treasure.  <br>
<br>
